<h2><a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/1155.html" title="Chautauqua weekend and lots of homework"> Chautauqua weekend and lots of homework</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p>So what else is new?</p>

	<p>Darlene&#8217;s packing for the <a href="http://www.madisonchautauqua.com">Madison Chautauqua</a>, the big art show that&#8217;s here in Madison this weekend. There was an article in the local monthly newspaper about her, but unfortunately it&#8217;s not available on the web.</p>

	<p>I&#8217;m busy with an information architecture course which starts with learning how to hand code websites. This is my <a href="http://library.ontheriversedge.com">projects</a> page if you&#8217;re interested. The only projects I&#8217;ve done so far that are interesting are ones about Darlene making pots and a website evaluation of the <a href="http://www.aucklandcitylibraries.com">Auckland City Libraries</a> website.</p>


 
